<h1>The legends of Kalamatian souvlakia</h1>

<div class = "description">
    <p> This webpage features the stories about 
    the legendary souvlakia of Kalamata - exactly <%= @articles.count%> distinct types of souvlaki 
    you can discover all around Kalamata. Dive in into the stories of souvlakia
    and learn everything about them yourself!</p>
</div>

<div id = "posts-container">
    <ul class = "articles">
        <% @articles.each do |article| %>
            <li>
            <%= link_to article.title, article %>
            <p class= "short-text"><%= article.short_text %></p>
            </li>
        <% end %>
    </ul>
</div>

<%= link_to '<button type="button">New Post</button>'.html_safe, new_article_path %>
